 exist as incomplete yet powerful sources.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aEnglish literaturexHistory and criticismyMiddle English, 1100-1500. 0aOld age in literature. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Medieval.2bisacsh  aCaxton.  aChaucer.  aDisability.  aHamlet.  aHoccleve.  aJohn Gower.  aMiddle English literature.  aPolonius.  aprosthesis.  arhetoric.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311074322708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021 Englishz978311075412408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021z9783110753899oZDB-23-DKU40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781641892551?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781641892551423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781641892551/original  a978-3-11-074322-7  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075412-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-DKUb2021